descript.abstract: Road ROW, Railroad ROW, and easements. Symbolize by Encumbrace type. Edited in Parcel fabric and exported to sde weekly. Also includes vacated and non active encumbrances. Use STATUS field to determine whether Active or not. There is a layer file for this in U:\GIS-Users\Layerfiles\CDSTRL\
